<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<title>
			{% block title %}Bienvenue sur le site d'Atamatoki!
			{% endblock %}
		</title>
		<link rel='stylesheet' href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css' integrity='sha512-GQGU0fMMi238uA+a/bdWJfpUGKUkBdgfFdgBm72SUQ6BeyWjoY/ton0tEjH+OSH9iP4Dfh+7HM0I9f5eR0L/4w==' crossorigin='anonymous'/>
		<link rel="icon" href="{{ asset('img/favicon.ico') }}" type="image/ico">
		<link rel='stylesheet' href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.css' integrity='sha512-4wFGk961cJS2gpSfzy1vU+R8Q93foZOoGgfEDetiClOqNvggdtnRpdCsAgfm8VU9mKkv2unla8RBYwA6hoFwqg==' crossorigin='anonymous'/>
		<link rel='stylesheet' href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/normalize/8.0.1/normalize.css' integrity='sha512-oHDEc8Xed4hiW6CxD7qjbnI+B07vDdX7hEPTvn9pSZO1bcRqHp8mj9pyr+8RVC2GmtEfI2Bi9Ke9Ass0as+zpg==' crossorigin='anonymous'/>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css/style.css') }}">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css/base-style.css') }}">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css/fonts.css') }}">
	</head>
	<body>
	<header>
		<div class="logo-and-tab">
			<a href="/" class="logo"><img src="{{ asset('img/banner-green.png') }}" alt="Logo du Projet"></a>
			<div class="header-tab">
				{% if not app.user %}
					<div class="non-authentificated">
						<a href="{{ path('security_login') }}" class="sign-up login">Se Connecter</a>
					</div>
					<div class="non-authentificated">
						<a href="{{ path('security_registration') }}" class="sign-up">S'inscrire</a>
					</div>
				{% else %}
					<div class="authentificated">
						<a href="{{ path('security_logout') }}" class="sign-up logout">Se Déconnecter</a>
					</div>
					{# <a href="/panier" class="cart">
						<i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i>
					</a> #}
				{% endif %}
			</div>
		</div>
		<nav>
			<a href="{{ path('home') }}" class="nav-home nav-animated">Accueil</a>
			<a href="{{ path('tracks') }}" class="nav-tracks nav-animated">Tracks</a>
			<a href="{{ path('atamatoki') }}" class="nav-ata nav-animated">L'artiste</a>
			<a href="{{ path('contact') }}" class="nav-contact nav-animated">Nous Contacter</a>
			{% if is_granted('ROLE_ADMIN') %}
				<a href="{{ path('admin_home')}}" class="nav-admin nav-animated">Page Admin</a>
			{% endif %}
		</nav>
	</header>
		<div class="container">
			{% block body %}{% endblock %}
		</div>
		<footer>
			{# <div class="info">
				<div class="info-details">
					<i class="fab fa-paypal"></i>
					<h3>Paiement Securisé</h3>
					<p>Chaque paiement s'effectue de manière sécurisée par Paypal. Vos données resteront confidentielles.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="info-details">
					<i class="fas fa-arrow-circle-down"></i>
					<h3>Téléchargement Immédiat</h3>
					<p>Une fois la licence achetée, un lien exclusif vous est délivré pour télécharger instantanément la production.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="info-details">
					<i class="fa-solid fa-file-waveform"></i>
					<h3>Instrumentales De Haute-Qualité</h3>
					<p>Chaque instrumentale est délivrée avec la meilleure qualité de son et un mixage travaillé, idéal tant pour travailler en studio que chez soi.</p>
				</div>
			</div> #}
			<div class="footer">
				<a href="/" class="footer-logo"><img src="{{ asset('img/banner-green.png') }}"/></a>
				<div class="footer-flex">
					<div class="footer-contact">
						<h4>Contact</h4>
						<ul class="contact">
							<li>
								<a href="mailto:atamatoki@gmail.com">Mail</a>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="footer-social">
						<h4>Reseaux</h4>
						<ul class="social-networks">
							<li>
								<a href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/2BzNGTZcU0rrEmwevE6FFM">
									<i class="fab fa-spotify"></i>
								</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="https://music.apple.com/us/artist/atamatoki/1486586364">
									<i class="fa-solid fa-music"></i>
								</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChjjiIV0wQZ4a_9-SEM572A">
									<i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i>
								</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="https://www.twitch.tv/atamatoki">
									<i class="fa-brands fa-twitch"></i>
								</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="https://www.instagram.com/atamatoki/">
									<i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
								</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="https://soundcloud.com/atama-toki">
									<i class="fab fa-soundcloud"></i>
								</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="https://twitter.com/atama_toki">
									<i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i>
								</a>
							</li>
							<li>
								<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@atamatoki">
									<i class="fa-brands fa-tiktok"></i>
								</a>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
